Do I care if I get rekt in crypto and NFTs in a downturn? No, was here in 2017. The second cycle is easier as the volatility seems normal.

One of the worst things about tradfi was after about 2 years you don't learn anything you just become a hamster in a wheel. Even at the highest levels of a CPA firm there was no challenge, just monotony. Crypto/NFTs provide challenge and learning.

The last 7 months in NFTs have been the most fun of my life üòÇ, what a time to be alive. Lived through the wild west era of a technology. As a learner type, I can't get enough. No time for sleep, too much to learn.
